    int M

Methods: 
     double do_bar(std::vector<double, std::allocator<double> >)  
           
R> 
R> bb <- new(Baz)
R> bb
C++ object <0x18c8f90> of class 'Baz' <0x1c37db0>
R> bb$M <- 12
